data.description: Seller willing to contribute to closing costs and/or rate buy down!! Relax on the elevated deck and enjoy the lake views! The property is fully fenced with a drive thru gate. Cement drive is 77' deep and with 45' covered! Open interior floor plan features vaulted ceilings... 2 bedrooms with 2 bathrooms... the kitchen has a gas stove...built in microwave...dishwasher and a casual dining area! Updated bathrooms featuring granite vanities and a custom tiled step in shower! The property backs to a wash for privacy. Enjoy the color filled sunsets from the deck and covered patio! The home also has an enclosed entry patio and a handy storage shed! Call your Realtor today for a tour!
